 The north is known for classy and carnival-like wedding ceremonies. Occasionally, there comes a celebration that leaves even the billionaires in attendance impressed. This was the atmosphere when the family of Fatima Abdulkadir Abacha, the niece of the late General Sani Abacha recently celebrated their daughter. Beautiful Fatima got married to her heartthrob, Sadiq Saleh Jambo, son of the late billionaire oil magnate Mallam Saleh Jambo in an event that had elites from the north and other parts of Nigeria in attendance. The wedding which took place at the Silverbird Private Chambers in Abuja had billionaire businessman, Prince Engineer Arthur Eze as the father of the day. It also had top dignitaries including politicians, businessmen and people from other works of life in attendance. Expectedly, the party was a feast of a sort with an assortment of vintage wines and dishes for guests in attendance. The post Fatima Abacha Holds Royal Wedding  Source: Independent 2 decades after the death of General Sani Abacha, it is important that we never forget his legacy. Today, June 8, 2018, marks the 20th anniversary of the death of General Sani Abacha. He was Nigeria&apos;s 10th Head of State. I remember the day the clearly. I had just gotten… June 8, 2018 In "News" The News Agency of Nigeria(NAN) reports that prominent Nigerians converged on Agodi Gardens in Ibadan on Saturday to celebrate with the couple and their families. Vice President Yemi Osinbajo and wife of President Muhammadu Buhari, Aisha Buhari were among the dignitaries that attended the wedding reception of Idris and Fatima… March 11, 2018 In "News" The OAP discusses the highbrow wedding and criticises Pastors in his Youtube video. Daddy Freeze dissects Jamil Abubakar and Fatima Dangote’s wedding shares more lessons.Aliko Dangote’s daughter, Fatima, exchanged marriage vows with Jamil, the son of former IGP Mohammed Dikko on March 23, 2018, at Eko Hotels and Suites, Victoria… March 26, 2018 In "News"